---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout title="Home">
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pt-24 pb-12">
    <div class="animate-in">
      <h1 class="text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight leading-tight mb-6" style="line-height:1.1">
        Figma x Contra
        <br />Makeathon Analysis
      </h1>
    </div>
    <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl leading-relaxed mb-8 animate-in animate-in-delay-1" style="line-height:1.7">
      Three editions. Thousands of participants. One question: what separates
      winners from the crowd? We analyzed every available data point to find out.
    </p>
    <div class="flex gap-4 animate-in animate-in-delay-2">
      <a href="/report" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl text-sm font-medium transition-all duration-200" style="background: #BA7517; color: #FFFFFF;">
        Read the Full Report
      </a>
      <a href="/charts" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 rounded-xl border border-border text-foreground text-sm font-medium hover:border-primary transition-all duration-200">
        Explore Charts
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 pb-20">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 mb-20">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 bg-card card-hover animate-in animate-in-delay-1">
        <div class="text-4xl font-medium text-primary mb-1 stat-number" style="line-height:1.1">21K+</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Total Participants</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 bg-card card-hover animate-in animate-in-delay-2">
        <div class="text-4xl font-medium text-primary mb-1 stat-number" style="line-height:1.1">3</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Makeathon Editions</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 bg-card card-hover animate-in animate-in-delay-3">
        <div class="text-4xl font-medium text-primary mb-1 stat-number" style="line-height:1.1">318</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Entries Analyzed</div>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 bg-card card-hover animate-in animate-in-delay-4">
        <div class="text-4xl font-medium text-primary mb-1 stat-number" style="line-height:1.1">$300K</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-muted-foreground">Total Prize Pool</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-medium mb-2 animate-in" style="line-height:1.2">What the Data Shows</h2>
    <p class="text-muted-foreground mb-8 animate-in animate-in-delay-1" style="line-height:1.7">Six patterns emerged when we compared winners against everyone else.</p>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 bg-card card-hover animate-in animate-in-delay-1">
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Early Posters Win More</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="line-height:1.7">
          Winners posted on average <strong class="text-foreground font-medium">Day 4.4</strong> of the submission window,
          compared to <strong class="text-foreground font-medium">Day 11.7</strong> for non-winners. A full week advantage.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 bg-card card-hover animate-in animate-in-delay-2">
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Engagement Gap is Massive</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="line-height:1.7">
          Winners averaged <strong class="text-foreground font-medium">8.7x</strong> more engagement
          (likes + comments) than non-winners.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 bg-card card-hover animate-in animate-in-delay-3">
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Cross-Platform Presence Pays Off</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="line-height:1.7">
          Winners cross-posted to <strong class="text-foreground font-medium">3.0 platforms</strong>
          vs <strong class="text-foreground font-medium">1.1</strong> for non-winners. Social amplification works.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border border-border p-6 bg-card card-hover animate-in animate-in-delay-4">
        <h3 class="font-medium mb-2">Zero Pre-Challenge Advantage</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-foreground" style="line-height:1.7">
          Our video date analysis found <strong class="text-foreground font-medium">no evidence</strong> of
          winners starting before the challenge. The advantage is early submissions within the window.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
